title: Yahyaabad, Khoshab
content:
Yahyaabad (Persian: يحيي اباد, also Romanized as Yaḩyáābād)[1] is a village in Tabas Rural District, in the Central District of Khoshab County, Razavi Khorasan Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 20, in 9 families.[2]
